caption:
🌅✨ “Golden hour, endless horizons.”
Jade, young and radiant, stands on a cliff overlooking the turquoise sea of Ischia, capturing the sunset with her camera. Her silk crop top and high-waisted denim shorts glow in the warm golden light. Friend Lucas holds a drone in the background while a local fisherman works nearby, completing the cinematic scene. Soft shadows, reflective shoreline, and a gentle breeze create the perfect dreamy atmosphere. 📸🌊
